FW Outlook Migration for Bill Rapp Cc Bill you will be migrated to our LAN Tuesday night and be able to access the ETS Lan Microsoft Outlook on Wednesday morning They told me you should be able to access Outlook on the EES LAN Monday and Tuesday until then so hopefully you wont miss any messages Im taking a vacation day tomorrow but will be back Monday so if you have any questions or problems tomorrow please call Denise Lagesse at or Ruth Mann at and they can help youSee you Monday Emily Sellers Enron Transportation Services Legal Smith Street EB Houston Tx mailto Original Message From Mangin Emmanuel Sent Thursday October AM To ETS Information Risk Management Cc Sellers Emily Wagner Glenda Fossum Drew Subject RE Outlook Migration for Bill Rapp Hi Lupita I would be happy to migrate Bill on Monday Oct nd but we are already well above our maximum number of migrations I can however migrate the following day Please confirm if this will work for you or if you whish to migrate at a later time Thanks E Original Message From ETS Information Risk Management Sent Wednesday October PM To Mangin Emmanuel Cc Sellers Emily Wagner Glenda ETS Information Risk Management Subject Outlook Migration for Bill Rapp Emmanuel Please schedule the Outlook migration for Bill Rapp for He is transferring from EES to ETS This is his info LoginID brapp FirstNameBill LastName Rapp Business Unit ETS Date of Move Thanks Lupita Cantu ETS Information Risk Management Original Message From Enron Messaging Security Sent Wednesday October PM To Fossum Drew Cc Cantu Lupita Subject ERequest Bill Rapp Bill Rapps mail will be migrated from Lotus Notes to Outlook by the Outlook Migration Team Please send an email to Emmanuel Mangin and provide the following information LoginID FirstName LastName Company or Business Unit and date of move Also please tell Emmanuel that Drew is moving from EES to ETS Many Thanks Lisa Scully

RE ComputerOkay thanks for getting back to me Emily Sellers Enron Transportation Services Legal Smith Street EB Houston Tx mailto Original Message From Rapp Bill Sent Monday October PM To Sellers Emily Subject Re Computer Emily Thanks for the email and I look forward to meeting you too I would prefer a laptop with a docking station I would also prefer to keep the same phone number that I have now Thanks again From Emily nronXgate on PM To Bill ES cc Greg nronXgate Subject Computer Bill I wanted to introduce myself Im Drew Fossums Assistant and let you know I will be taking care of getting you moved to our group on October nd I have most of the information already from HR but I wanted to ask you if you prefer a desktop computer or laptop with a docking station and if you want to keep your same phone number I want to order a computer as soon as possible so you will have it when you moveYour new office location will be EB which were hoping to have cleared out before the nd in case you want to move some things before then I look forward to meeting you in person and if you have any questions please feel free to call or email me Thanks Emily Sellers Enron Transportation Services Legal Smith Street EB Houston Tx File aleabanrgif File Leaves Bkgrdjpg
